    <h2 class="mc mike-friends-blog"><strong>Mike &amp; Friends Blog</strong></h2>

    
      <div class="blogger">
        <a href="/blogger/raymcgovern">
          <img class="blogshot" src="https://dwoq5s27enw2w.cloudfront.net/uploads/blogshots/ray-64x64.jpg"/>
